---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Services - Points Beyond">
  <section class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Services</h1>
      <p>AI-optimized strategies for the modern search landscape</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="services">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="service">
        <div class="service-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8"/><path d="m21 21-4.3-4.3"/><path d="M11 8v6"/><path d="M8 11h6"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="service-content">
          <h2>Answer Engine Optimization (AEO)</h2>
          <p class="service-intro">
            The way people find information has fundamentally changed. When someone asks ChatGPT, Perplexity, Claude, or Google AI Overview a question about your industry, your content should be the answer they receive.
          </p>
          <p>
            Answer Engine Optimization positions your brand as the authoritative source that AI systems cite when responding to user queries. Unlike traditional SEO which optimizes for link clicks, AEO focuses on becoming the definitive answer—the content AI trusts enough to quote directly.
          </p>
          <h3>What We Deliver</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Get Found When Customers Ask AI</strong> — We make sure your business shows up when people ask ChatGPT, Google, or Siri for recommendations in your area</li>
            <li><strong>Answer the Questions Your Customers Actually Ask</strong> — We optimize your content around the real questions people type into AI and search engines</li>
            <li><strong>Stand Out in AI Recommendations</strong> — Position your business ahead of competitors when AI suggests local services</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="service">
        <div class="service-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="22 12 18 12 15 21 9 3 6 12 2 12"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="service-content">
          <h2>Search Engine Optimization (SEO)</h2>
          <p class="service-intro">
            Traditional search isn't going away—it's evolving. Google still processes billions of searches daily, and ranking well remains essential for visibility, credibility, and traffic.
          </p>
          <p>
            We combine proven SEO fundamentals with AI-era strategies to ensure your content performs across both conventional search results and the new AI-curated responses appearing at the top of search pages. Our approach builds sustainable organic visibility that compounds over time.
          </p>
          <h3>What We Deliver</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Google Business Profile Optimization</strong> — Get your business listing fully optimized so you show up in local searches and Google Maps</li>
            <li><strong>Rank Higher in Local Search</strong> — We help you appear when customers search for services like yours in your area</li>
            <li><strong>Website Tune-Up</strong> — Make sure your site loads fast, works on phones, and tells Google exactly what you do</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="service">
        <div class="service-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="service-content">
          <h2>AI Voice Receptionist</h2>
          <p class="service-intro">
            Never miss a call again. Our AI Voice Receptionist answers your business phone 24/7 with natural, human-like conversation—booking appointments, answering FAQs, and ensuring every caller gets immediate attention.
          </p>
          <p>
            Unlike basic voicemail or rigid phone trees, our AI receptionist handles real conversations. It understands context, manages interruptions, and adapts to each caller's needs. Your customers get instant service while you focus on running your business.
          </p>
          <h3>What We Deliver</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Never Miss a Call</strong> — Every call answered instantly, 24/7, even nights, weekends, and holidays</li>
            <li><strong>Book Appointments Automatically</strong> — Callers can schedule, reschedule, or confirm appointments without you lifting a finger</li>
            <li><strong>Answer Customer Questions</strong> — Hours, pricing, services, directions—handled instantly so you don't have to</li>
            <li><strong>Get Call Summaries</strong> — Know exactly what was discussed with transcripts delivered to your inbox</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-card">
        <h2>Let's Build Your AI Strategy</h2>
        <p>Every business has unique needs. Let's explore how Points Beyond can help you thrive in the AI era.</p>
        <a href="/points-beyond/contact/" class="cta">Contact Us</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-header {
    padding: 3rem 2rem 1.5rem;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
  }

  .page-header::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.15) 0%, transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .page-header h1 {
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e2e8f0 0%, #a78bfa 50%, #8b5cf6 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
    position: relative;
  }

  .page-header p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }

  .services {
    padding: 1rem 2rem 2.5rem;
  }

  .service {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    padding: 1.25rem;
    background: var(--color-card-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-card-border);
    border-radius: 16px;
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  }

  .service-icon {
    color: var(--color-primary-light);
    flex-shrink: 0;
    padding-top: 0.25rem;
  }

  .service-content h2 {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .service-content h3 {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--color-primary-light);
  }

  .service-intro {
    color: var(--color-text);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .service-content p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .service-content ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .service-content li {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    padding: 0.5rem 0;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
    line-height: 1.5;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-card-border);
  }

  .service-content li:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .service-content li::before {
    content: "→";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--color-primary-light);
  }

  .service-content li strong {
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .cta-section {
    padding: 0.5rem 2rem 2rem;
  }

  .cta-card {
    background: var(--color-card-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-card-border);
    border-radius: 24px;
    padding: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  }

  .cta-card h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .cta-card p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .cta {
    display: inline-block;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary) 0%, var(--color-primary-dark) 100%);
    color: white;
    padding: 1rem 2.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 1rem;
    transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
  }

  .cta:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.4);
    color: white;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .page-header {
      padding: 2rem 1rem;
    }

    .page-header h1 {
      font-size: 1.75rem;
    }

    .services {
      padding: 1.5rem 1rem;
    }

    .service {
      flex-direction: row;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 0.75rem;
      padding: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .service-icon {
      padding-top: 0.1rem;
    }

    .service-icon svg {
      width: 24px;
      height: 24px;
    }

    .service-content h2 {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .service-content h3 {
      margin-top: 0.75rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
    }

    .service-intro {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .cta-section {
      padding: 1.5rem 1rem;
    }

    .cta-card {
      padding: 1.5rem 1rem;
    }

    .cta-card h2 {
      font-size: 1.4rem;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .cta {
      padding: 0.875rem 2rem;
      width: 100%;
      text-align: center;
    }
  }
</style>
